1
00:01:41,160 --> 00:01:42,040
Run!

2
00:01:42,080 --> 00:01:43,420
Don't lose to that cloud!

3
00:01:46,180 --> 00:01:47,340
Let's stop here.

4
00:01:47,380 --> 00:01:48,380
There's no way ahead.

5
00:01:48,420 --> 00:01:50,840
Yingtao, no more white geese.

6
00:01:50,880 --> 00:01:52,340
Let's go back and play games.

7
00:01:52,840 --> 00:01:53,680
I can fly over.

8
00:01:54,180 --> 00:01:55,360
The book says

9
00:01:55,400 --> 00:01:56,640
if you jump hard enough,

10
00:01:56,680 --> 00:01:58,020
and far enough,

11
00:01:58,060 --> 00:01:59,480
wings will grow on your back,

12
00:02:00,300 --> 00:02:01,260
and then…

13
00:02:05,900 --> 00:02:06,860
What are you two doing?

14
00:02:07,620 --> 00:02:09,380
Lin Yingtao, go back now

15
00:02:09,419 --> 00:02:11,280
or I won't let you copy my homework again.

16
00:02:11,320 --> 00:02:12,660
My dad told me

17
00:02:12,700 --> 00:02:14,080
that a real top student's

18
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:15,720
moving to our construction site soon.

19
00:02:15,760 --> 00:02:16,900
Their family's getting

20
00:02:16,940 --> 00:02:18,180
a unit right next to mine.

21
00:02:18,220 --> 00:02:19,160
So if you cut me off,

22
00:02:19,200 --> 00:02:20,240
I have other options.

23
00:02:21,140 --> 00:02:23,240
Son, we'll arrive at Qunshan soon.

24
00:02:24,120 --> 00:02:25,020
Stop drawing now.

25
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:28,440
Earlier you weren't feeling well
after eating on the way.

26
00:02:28,480 --> 00:02:29,440
Get some rest.

27
00:02:29,940 --> 00:02:32,080
There's an entrance exam when we arrive.

28
00:02:39,480 --> 00:02:41,060
What's with the dirty coat?

29
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:43,040
If it's your favorite,

30
00:02:43,080 --> 00:02:44,240
I can get you a new one.

31
00:02:47,820 --> 00:02:49,100
Yingtao, slow down!

32
00:02:59,420 --> 00:03:01,260
Stick. Find a stick.

33
00:03:02,540 --> 00:03:04,280
A startled snake will bite.

34
00:03:09,120 --> 00:03:10,380
That snake jumped

35
00:03:11,180 --> 00:03:12,140
higher than me.

36
00:03:12,680 --> 00:03:13,780
Exactly!

37
00:03:13,820 --> 00:03:15,920
Lin Yingtao,
you really need to grow taller.

38
00:03:16,800 --> 00:03:18,240
Even snakes can jump higher than you.

39
00:03:19,680 --> 00:03:20,760
This is it.

40
00:03:20,800 --> 00:03:22,140
I'm finished!

41
00:03:22,180 --> 00:03:23,020
Yingtao!

42
00:03:38,080 --> 00:03:39,320
I need to use my time wisely

43
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:40,440
and do something meaningful.

44
00:03:40,480 --> 00:03:42,380
What meaning is there

45
00:03:42,420 --> 00:03:44,080
in helping Cai Fangyuan steal the book?

46
00:03:44,120 --> 00:03:45,340
Of course, it's meaningful.

47
00:03:46,280 --> 00:03:48,020
That novel is mine.

48
00:03:48,600 --> 00:03:50,260
Did you reach it yet?

49
00:03:50,300 --> 00:03:51,520
I'm almost out of strength.

50
00:04:35,500 --> 00:04:36,340
Hello.

51
00:04:41,900 --> 00:04:43,380
Yingtao, where is my book?

52
00:04:43,920 --> 00:04:45,880
- Run.
- Run.

53
00:05:07,600 --> 00:05:08,440
- Mom.
- Hey.

54
00:05:08,980 --> 00:05:10,120
What's wrong, Yingtao?

55
00:05:11,440 --> 00:05:12,520
Mom.

56
00:05:12,560 --> 00:05:13,400
What if…

57
00:05:13,440 --> 00:05:14,800
What if someone

58
00:05:14,840 --> 00:05:16,220
tries to take me away

59
00:05:16,260 --> 00:05:18,220
to a place without you?

60
00:05:18,760 --> 00:05:20,060
Who's trying to take you?

61
00:05:20,660 --> 00:05:21,820
Tell me who you met.

62
00:05:21,860 --> 00:05:23,400
I mean if.

63
00:05:23,440 --> 00:05:25,720
Just like Rapunzel was taken

64
00:05:25,760 --> 00:05:27,300
to another world by a witch.

65
00:05:28,380 --> 00:05:29,500
You're safe.

66
00:05:29,540 --> 00:05:31,340
No one can take you from us.

67
00:05:31,380 --> 00:05:32,500
Juan!

68
00:05:33,480 --> 00:05:35,000
Prepare two more dishes tonight.

69
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:36,700
- Manager Jiang's here.
- It smells so good.

70
00:05:36,740 --> 00:05:38,480
- Sorry to barge in, Shengjuan.
- Look who's here.

71
00:05:38,520 --> 00:05:39,960
- Manager Jiang.
- Little Yingtao.

72
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:40,960
Have you gain some weight?

73
00:05:41,540 --> 00:05:42,660
Yingtao.

74
00:05:42,700 --> 00:05:43,540
Say hello.

75
00:05:44,680 --> 00:05:45,560
Manager Jiang.

76
00:05:46,120 --> 00:05:46,960
Come on.

77
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:48,020
Drink.

78
00:05:48,060 --> 00:05:48,900
Drink!
No.

79
00:05:49,940 --> 00:05:51,040
- Fine.
- Drink slower.

80
00:05:51,080 --> 00:05:52,200
It's okay.

81
00:05:52,240 --> 00:05:53,500
Qiaoxi, you're eating.

82
00:05:53,540 --> 00:05:55,060
Why're you wearing the backpack?

83
00:05:55,100 --> 00:05:56,020
Take it off.

84
00:05:56,720 --> 00:05:57,620
Qiaoxi,

85
00:05:57,660 --> 00:05:59,100
could you take off your backpack?

86
00:06:01,860 --> 00:06:03,060
What's wrong?

87
00:06:03,600 --> 00:06:04,800
Inside his backpack

88
00:06:04,840 --> 00:06:06,020
is a jacket his cousin

89
00:06:06,060 --> 00:06:07,060
from Hong Kong bought him.

90
00:06:07,100 --> 00:06:09,080
It got dirty on the trip here,

91
00:06:09,120 --> 00:06:10,140
so I told him

92
00:06:10,180 --> 00:06:11,280
to toss it,

93
00:06:11,320 --> 00:06:12,380
but he wouldn't.

94
00:06:12,420 --> 00:06:14,140
So he just stuffed it in his bag

95
00:06:14,180 --> 00:06:15,020
and took it here.

96
00:06:16,020 --> 00:06:17,340
It's alright, Qiaoxi.

97
00:06:17,380 --> 00:06:19,060
How about Auntie washes it for you?

98
00:06:19,100 --> 00:06:20,940
By tomorrow when it's dry,
you can wear it again.

99
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:25,380
Yingtao.

100
00:06:26,020 --> 00:06:27,360
We're out of laundry detergent.

101
00:06:27,400 --> 00:06:28,860
Can you help Mom

102
00:06:28,900 --> 00:06:30,000
buy a pack

103
00:06:30,040 --> 00:06:31,560
from Uncle Qin's shop?

104
00:06:36,620 --> 00:06:39,320
- Uncle Qin, a pack of laundry detergent.
- Hey, Stella.

105
00:06:42,020 --> 00:06:44,240
DAILY GOODS, GROCERIES & CIGARETTES,
CHILDREN'S TOYS, ICE CREAM & SODAS

106
00:06:44,280 --> 00:06:45,840
My dad's out getting supplies.

107
00:06:46,340 --> 00:06:47,300
Lin Yingtao,

108
00:06:47,340 --> 00:06:49,640
I heard you cried over a snake today.

109
00:06:49,680 --> 00:06:51,880
Fell on the ground face down a few times.

110
00:06:52,800 --> 00:06:53,780
Laundry detergent.

111
00:07:01,260 --> 00:07:03,160
Lin Yingtao, I stepped on your shadow.

112
00:07:03,200 --> 00:07:04,240
I won!

113
00:07:04,860 --> 00:07:06,220
I'm too lazy to bother with you.

114
00:07:07,080 --> 00:07:07,980
Is that a surrender?

115
00:07:08,520 --> 00:07:10,380
I met foes that make you look weak.

116
00:07:11,260 --> 00:07:13,220
Can you handle him? How?

117
00:07:13,940 --> 00:07:14,800
I can't.

118
00:07:14,840 --> 00:07:16,720
You're just a bully who picks on the weak.

119
00:07:17,580 --> 00:07:18,700
You don't understand.

120
00:07:18,740 --> 00:07:20,340
He's on another level.

121
00:07:20,840 --> 00:07:22,160
Who cares?

122
00:07:22,200 --> 00:07:23,720
"Enemies aren't for fearing.

123
00:07:23,760 --> 00:07:25,120
They're for fighting."

124
00:07:25,160 --> 00:07:26,540
Your words.

125
00:07:26,580 --> 00:07:28,280
Qin Yeyun. Look over there.

126
00:07:29,320 --> 00:07:30,920
I stepped on your shadow too.

127
00:07:30,960 --> 00:07:32,200
No way I'm losing to you.

128
00:07:33,020 --> 00:07:34,320
Lin Yingtao!

129
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:40,120
Have a seat.

130
00:07:51,420 --> 00:07:52,680
Want some candies?

131
00:07:56,340 --> 00:07:57,840
Or do you want to
listen to some cassettes?

132
00:07:59,400 --> 00:08:02,180
Give me one cup of Oblivion's brew.

133
00:08:03,940 --> 00:08:06,040
Mickey Mouse. Care to read it?

134
00:08:06,080 --> 00:08:08,420
Everyone loves to read Mickey Mouse.

135
00:08:34,220 --> 00:08:35,580
Chunlu.

136
00:08:35,620 --> 00:08:38,480
For now, just stay
in this little nest of yours.

137
00:08:38,980 --> 00:08:40,159
No wandering off.

138
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:41,400
Mom's to keep you safe.

139
00:08:47,980 --> 00:08:48,980
Chunlu!

140
00:09:02,900 --> 00:09:04,080
Chunlu.

141
00:09:13,260 --> 00:09:14,360
Let me show you.

142
00:09:15,480 --> 00:09:17,480
Hold it like this first,

143
00:09:18,220 --> 00:09:19,440
then…

144
00:09:20,000 --> 00:09:20,920
pet it…

145
00:09:21,420 --> 00:09:22,420
this way.

146
00:10:00,400 --> 00:10:02,020
Have you found that Qiaoxi

147
00:10:02,060 --> 00:10:03,200
is different from

148
00:10:03,240 --> 00:10:04,460
other children?

149
00:10:04,500 --> 00:10:05,420
Of course.

150
00:10:05,920 --> 00:10:07,440
He is a boy genius on math.

151
00:10:07,480 --> 00:10:08,340
Sure he is different.

152
00:10:08,840 --> 00:10:09,960
I think

153
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:12,420
he never really moved on
from what happened to his family

154
00:10:12,920 --> 00:10:14,040
decades ago.

155
00:10:14,540 --> 00:10:16,020
Listen, Juan,

156
00:10:16,060 --> 00:10:17,820
let's not bring up

157
00:10:17,860 --> 00:10:19,860
what others avoid discussing.

158
00:10:22,100 --> 00:10:23,800
Manager Jiang has enough on his plate.

159
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:25,720
We should show this child more compassion.

160
00:10:25,760 --> 00:10:26,600
Okay.

161
00:10:28,700 --> 00:10:30,740
Come on, enough already!

162
00:10:32,860 --> 00:10:33,940
A kid

163
00:10:33,980 --> 00:10:36,060
ate something bad and threw up.

164
00:10:36,100 --> 00:10:37,420
That's normal, right?

165
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:40,180
He's fine now.

166
00:10:40,220 --> 00:10:41,580
We ate dinner over

167
00:10:41,620 --> 00:10:43,360
at Electrician Lin's,

168
00:10:43,400 --> 00:10:45,280
even played for a bit afterwards.

169
00:10:45,960 --> 00:10:47,620
Alright. Spare me the drama.

170
00:11:34,840 --> 00:11:35,920
Yingtao.

171
00:11:35,960 --> 00:11:37,520
Is that new student next door really

172
00:11:37,560 --> 00:11:38,740
as hardcore as they say?

173
00:11:39,340 --> 00:11:41,100
My dad said that he went to your home,

174
00:11:41,140 --> 00:11:43,040
still grinding homework past midnight.

175
00:11:43,080 --> 00:11:44,120
There's something

176
00:11:44,160 --> 00:11:45,480
I need to come clean about.

177
00:11:46,200 --> 00:11:47,040
What?

178
00:11:47,580 --> 00:11:48,640
That new student,

179
00:11:48,680 --> 00:11:50,420
you must treat him well.

180
00:11:50,460 --> 00:11:52,000
Make sure he feels how friendly

181
00:11:52,040 --> 00:11:53,380
we are at Qunshan Elementary,

182
00:11:53,420 --> 00:11:54,720
and how kind Qunshan people can be.

183
00:11:54,760 --> 00:11:55,600
QUNSHAN POWER PLANT ELEMENTARY SCHOOL

184
00:11:55,640 --> 00:11:57,880
Lin Yingtao, are you serious?

185
00:11:57,920 --> 00:11:59,180
It's his first day,

186
00:11:59,220 --> 00:12:00,140
not a royal visit.

187
00:12:00,180 --> 00:12:01,620
You don't understand.

188
00:12:01,660 --> 00:12:03,500
if he leaves, I leave too.

189
00:12:03,540 --> 00:12:04,380
Where?

190
00:12:10,480 --> 00:12:12,620
Son, the principal

191
00:12:12,660 --> 00:12:14,080
has finally agreed to let you

192
00:12:14,120 --> 00:12:15,480
enroll first and take the test later.

193
00:12:16,020 --> 00:12:17,500
You have to take it seriously,

194
00:12:18,340 --> 00:12:19,580
no more acting out

195
00:12:19,620 --> 00:12:20,660
when the time comes.

196
00:12:30,300 --> 00:12:32,200
Two tiger moms,

197
00:12:32,240 --> 00:12:33,700
two tiger moms,

198
00:12:33,740 --> 00:12:35,780
Fighting hard,

199
00:12:35,820 --> 00:12:37,920
fighting hard!

200
00:12:37,960 --> 00:12:39,940
One lost her ears,

201
00:12:39,980 --> 00:12:41,960
one lost her tail,

202
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:45,820
- How bizarre!
- Are you idiot?

203
00:12:45,860 --> 00:12:46,700
You beat me first!

204
00:12:46,740 --> 00:12:47,740
What's this?

205
00:12:47,780 --> 00:12:49,060
Who's causing chaos?

206
00:12:50,640 --> 00:12:52,820
Lin Qile, stop messing around!

207
00:12:53,880 --> 00:12:55,960
Class has begun! Back to your seat!

208
00:12:56,000 --> 00:12:57,940
They even renamed you as "Qile",

209
00:12:57,980 --> 00:12:59,380
why can't you bring some joy?

210
00:13:01,400 --> 00:13:02,900
First day of school…

211
00:13:11,620 --> 00:13:13,540
This whole area is staff housing,

212
00:13:13,580 --> 00:13:14,680
ours included.

213
00:13:15,360 --> 00:13:17,540
Du Shang lives here too, in the

214
00:13:18,040 --> 00:13:19,400
single-occupancy dorm with his mom.

215
00:13:20,520 --> 00:13:22,380
His dad got transferred

216
00:13:22,420 --> 00:13:24,180
to the Pucheng construction site.

217
00:13:24,680 --> 00:13:26,320
Every time Uncle Du comes back,

218
00:13:26,360 --> 00:13:28,500
Du Shang gets moody for days.

219
00:13:28,540 --> 00:13:31,520
Probably upset Uncle Du
never brings gifts.

220
00:13:32,400 --> 00:13:34,160
That's Qin Yeyun's place.

221
00:13:34,200 --> 00:13:36,940
She's the person I hate most
in the whole world.

222
00:13:36,980 --> 00:13:39,180
She's got that clap-strike palm,
hits like a truck.

223
00:13:40,540 --> 00:13:41,800
But she's so pretty.

224
00:13:42,440 --> 00:13:44,660
Yu Qiao says we're
"two sides of the same coin".

225
00:13:44,700 --> 00:13:46,060
She's the bad side.

226
00:13:46,100 --> 00:13:47,060
I'm the shiny one.

227
00:13:49,680 --> 00:13:51,920
She lives with her dad.

228
00:13:51,960 --> 00:13:53,440
Ever seen him?

229
00:13:53,480 --> 00:13:55,220
Uncle Qin, who runs the kiosk.

230
00:13:55,720 --> 00:13:58,060
He got work injuries years ago,

231
00:13:58,100 --> 00:13:59,740
leaving him inconvenience of only one leg.

232
00:14:00,240 --> 00:14:01,580
Cai Fangyuan's dad let him

233
00:14:01,620 --> 00:14:03,720
take over the worksite concession stand.

234
00:14:03,760 --> 00:14:05,520
Uncle Qin is amazing.

235
00:14:05,560 --> 00:14:07,400
He does qigong every day to heal his leg.

236
00:14:10,420 --> 00:14:12,100
This is Yu Qiao's place,

237
00:14:12,140 --> 00:14:13,180
your deskmate.

238
00:14:13,220 --> 00:14:15,420
Sick dunk! That was legit!

239
00:14:15,460 --> 00:14:17,180
He lives with his dad,

240
00:14:17,220 --> 00:14:18,900
mom, grandma,

241
00:14:18,940 --> 00:14:21,000
and his little cousin Yu Jin.

242
00:14:22,060 --> 00:14:23,480
Yu Jin's mother fell ill,

243
00:14:23,520 --> 00:14:25,840
so she sent him to stay with them.

244
00:14:25,880 --> 00:14:27,940
Truth is, the Yu family's place
is already packed,

245
00:14:27,980 --> 00:14:29,520
no room to spare.

246
00:14:30,060 --> 00:14:31,560
But Uncle Yu is a Model Worker,

247
00:14:31,600 --> 00:14:33,280
the site's most respected veteran.

248
00:14:33,320 --> 00:14:34,680
He'd never say no to anyone.

249
00:14:35,860 --> 00:14:38,080
Next door to Yu Qiao's place
lives Cai Fangyuan,

250
00:14:38,120 --> 00:14:41,100
with his mom and dad.

251
00:14:41,140 --> 00:14:43,220
He's all about good food,

252
00:14:43,260 --> 00:14:44,680
fun games, and cool stuff.

253
00:14:45,460 --> 00:14:46,640
Auntie Kang's a killer cook,

254
00:14:46,680 --> 00:14:48,680
while Uncle Cai's a stock market whiz.

255
00:14:48,720 --> 00:14:51,240
They hope he can study hard,

256
00:14:51,280 --> 00:14:52,680
crack a top-tier university.

257
00:14:52,720 --> 00:14:53,700
BRUTE MOTO

258
00:14:54,620 --> 00:14:56,940
There's a bird's nest
up that big locust tree.

259
00:14:56,980 --> 00:14:59,300
Two years ago, a baby bird fell from it.

260
00:14:59,340 --> 00:15:00,200
I took it home,

261
00:15:00,240 --> 00:15:01,360
and my dad actually

262
00:15:01,400 --> 00:15:02,700
nursed it back to life.

263
00:15:03,200 --> 00:15:04,040
Well,

264
00:15:04,080 --> 00:15:06,440
the tree blooms with sweet white flowers
in spring.

265
00:15:06,480 --> 00:15:08,480
Mom used to make the best
steamed rice with them.

266
00:15:08,980 --> 00:15:11,180
The field in the west
still grows so many dandelions,

267
00:15:11,680 --> 00:15:13,300
but I've never liked them.

268
00:15:13,340 --> 00:15:14,500
They scatter easily.

269
00:15:21,280 --> 00:15:22,280
They say

270
00:15:22,780 --> 00:15:24,500
when someone goes to the other side,

271
00:15:25,000 --> 00:15:27,120
they forget everything from this life.

272
00:15:27,740 --> 00:15:29,200
I don't want to forget them,

273
00:15:29,840 --> 00:15:31,460
forget anything about Qunshan.

274
00:15:32,740 --> 00:15:34,480
Will you remember it all for me?

275
00:15:34,980 --> 00:15:36,160
If I forget,

276
00:15:36,200 --> 00:15:37,360
then you tell me.

277
00:15:38,660 --> 00:15:39,680
Doesn't remembering

278
00:15:40,680 --> 00:15:41,560
hurt even more?

279
00:15:41,600 --> 00:15:42,880
I'm not scared of pain.

280
00:15:42,920 --> 00:15:44,820
I don't even cry getting an injection.

281
00:15:45,840 --> 00:15:46,940
I just…

282
00:15:47,440 --> 00:15:49,620
I don't know if Mom and Dad

283
00:15:49,660 --> 00:15:52,040
will still love me after I die.

