496
00:27:15,860 --> 00:27:16,740
You silly thing!

497
00:27:16,780 --> 00:27:18,480
Why'd you listen so literally?

498
00:27:18,520 --> 00:27:19,740
What if I'm a bad guy?

499
00:27:20,540 --> 00:27:21,940
