513
00:28:00,900 --> 00:28:03,580
As Qiáo, "a peak, high and sharp".

514
00:28:04,080 --> 00:28:06,040
Qiaoxi. Here, west of the highest,

515
00:28:06,080 --> 00:28:08,240
sharpest summit in the Qunshan range.

516
00:28:08,280 --> 00:28:10,560
I once saw the most
breathtaking sunset clouds here.

517
00:28:11,100 --> 00:28:12,600
Crimson, blazing, glorious.

518
00:28:13,420 --> 00:28:15,740
I think that's what your name was meant.

519
00:28:16,740 --> 00:28:17,900
But now…

520
00:28:18,680 --> 00:28:20,640
Now it rains.

521
00:28:21,140 --> 00:28:22,320
And nothing can be seen.

522
00:28:23,260 --> 00:28:25,440
Then tell me the most beautiful sunset

523
00:28:25,480 --> 00:28:27,040
you have ever seen here.

524
00:28:27,640 --> 00:28:28,920
Then I'll tell you.

525
00:28:28,960 --> 00:28:31,140
That sunset burned like wildfire.

526
00:28:31,640 --> 00:28:33,980
Its shapes and hues morphing so wildly.

527
00:28:34,640 --> 00:28:36,480
I could never guess what it would

528
00:28:36,520 --> 00:28:38,020
look like in the next minute.

529
00:28:38,900 --> 00:28:40,620
Did it ever look like a rabbit?

530
00:28:40,660 --> 00:28:42,060
Yes.

531
00:28:42,100 --> 00:28:44,580
