559
00:30:12,020 --> 00:30:13,420
Wang Yu, don't drink it.

560
00:30:13,460 --> 00:30:15,760
It's not only non-toxic and harmless,

561
00:30:15,800 --> 00:30:17,720
- but also has a good cleaning…
- Uncle Wang.

562
00:30:18,380 --> 00:30:19,780
- Yingtao, you're back.
- Yingtao's back.

563
00:30:19,820 --> 00:30:22,020
Uncle Wang, where have you been?

564
00:30:22,060 --> 00:30:25,340
When you're gone, no one plays
"The Cow on the High Mountain" with me.

565
00:30:26,120 --> 00:30:27,700
Then let's play. Come on.

566
00:30:28,200 --> 00:30:31,180
On the high mountain stands a cow,

567
00:30:31,220 --> 00:30:33,820
Two curved horns upon its brow,

568
00:30:33,860 --> 00:30:36,340
Four hooves split eight ways neat,

569
00:30:36,380 --> 00:30:38,920
Tail out back, what a feat!

570
00:30:39,800 --> 00:30:41,080
Out back!

571
00:30:41,920 --> 00:30:43,180
Out back!

572
00:30:43,220 --> 00:30:44,100
Yingtao.

573
00:30:44,140 --> 00:30:45,160
Stop pestering your uncle.

574
00:30:45,200 --> 00:30:46,200
Go wash your hands and eat.

575
00:30:46,240 --> 00:30:47,880
Go, Yingtao.

576
00:30:48,380 --> 00:30:49,380
Uncle,

577
00:30:49,420 --> 00:30:51,440
are you having dinner here today?

578
00:30:51,480 --> 00:30:53,080
I'll eat faster than you this time.

579
00:30:53,740 --> 00:30:54,580
Of course.

580
00:30:54,620 --> 00:30:56,480
Your uncle will have dinner with us.

581
00:30:56,520 --> 00:30:57,620
Food's ready.

582
00:30:59,160 --> 00:31:02,300
Brother, Sis-in-law, I won't eat here.

583
00:31:02,340 --> 00:31:04,200
I have a lot of things to do.
I'm very busy.

584
00:31:09,800 --> 00:31:10,820
Wang Yu.

585
00:31:12,380 --> 00:31:15,400
- Wang Yu, we'll grab three bottles.
- Shall we eat?

586
00:31:15,440 --> 00:31:16,520
- I think it's good.
- Come.

587
00:31:16,560 --> 00:31:17,660
We'll give it a try.

588
00:31:18,700 --> 00:31:19,740
Well…

589
00:31:19,780 --> 00:31:20,760
Well…

590
00:31:25,600 --> 00:31:26,920
Stay for lunch.

591
00:31:26,960 --> 00:31:28,100
Let's eat together.

592
00:31:30,580 --> 00:31:32,500
This can be engraved with patterns.

593
00:31:33,240 --> 00:31:35,160
Where is Du Shang?

594
00:31:35,200 --> 00:31:36,820
We literally agreed

595
00:31:36,860 --> 00:31:39,400
to go up the mountain together,
early birthday for Qiaoxi,

596
00:31:39,440 --> 00:31:40,480
gifts ready.

597
00:31:40,980 --> 00:31:43,020
Is Du Shang's surprise
just not showing up?

598
00:31:43,060 --> 00:31:44,880
Cao Shuangyan,
what the hell is your problem?

599
00:31:44,920 --> 00:31:45,840
How could you do this?

600
00:31:45,880 --> 00:31:46,920
I've been breaking my back out there,

601
00:31:46,960 --> 00:31:48,340
finally come home.

602
00:31:48,380 --> 00:31:49,740
- The pork trotters won't even soften!
- Stop!

603
00:31:49,780 --> 00:31:51,120
You just don't want me back.

604
00:31:51,160 --> 00:31:51,840
- Right?
- Don't do this!

605
00:31:51,880 --> 00:31:53,940
It's because the gas tank is empty.

606
00:31:53,980 --> 00:31:55,840
Why does this always happen
when you come back?

607
00:31:55,880 --> 00:31:56,700
The gas tank's empty.

608
00:31:56,740 --> 00:31:58,280
Her brain is empty too?
Why not replace it?

609
00:31:58,320 --> 00:32:00,200
- Can you calm down?
- Dad.

610
00:32:00,240 --> 00:32:02,160
Dad, please stop hitting Mom.

611
00:32:02,200 --> 00:32:03,440
She's bleeding.

612
00:32:03,480 --> 00:32:04,540
You're still taking her side?

613
00:32:04,580 --> 00:32:06,080
Do you know who puts food on this table?

614
00:32:06,120 --> 00:32:07,040
You father, me!

615
00:32:07,080 --> 00:32:08,160
Get out of my face!

616
00:32:08,200 --> 00:32:09,360
What are you doing?

617
00:32:09,400 --> 00:32:10,480
Du Yongchun!

618
00:32:10,520 --> 00:32:12,200
- What are you doing?
- Did you teach him to say that?

619
00:32:12,240 --> 00:32:13,120
What are you doing?

620
00:32:13,160 --> 00:32:14,420
- I will beat you…
- Stop!

621
00:32:14,460 --> 00:32:15,340
- Hey stop!
- Stop!

622
00:32:17,180 --> 00:32:18,200
- Get off!
- Mom!

623
00:32:18,240 --> 00:32:19,360
Your medical expenses

624
00:32:19,400 --> 00:32:21,240
will be deducted from his bonus.

625
00:32:22,200 --> 00:32:23,300
Don't worry.

626
00:32:28,780 --> 00:32:30,600
Du Yongchun,
you'd better explain yourself.

627
00:32:30,640 --> 00:32:31,700
Why did you hit your wife?

628
00:32:32,200 --> 00:32:33,360
How did she deserve that?

629
00:32:35,700 --> 00:32:37,120
Manager Jiang, I drank too much.

630
00:32:43,740 --> 00:32:48,620
QUNSHAN NO.2 HOSPITAL

631
00:32:48,660 --> 00:32:49,500
Here's what we'll do.

632
00:32:49,540 --> 00:32:51,940
Divide Du Yongchun's wages
in three portions.

633
00:32:51,980 --> 00:32:53,400
Two portions sent home to his family,

634
00:32:53,440 --> 00:32:55,400
one kept for himself.

635
00:32:56,140 --> 00:32:58,460
And notify the worksite foreman,

636
00:32:58,500 --> 00:32:59,920
tell him I authorized this.

637
00:33:00,740 --> 00:33:01,900
Good, settled.

638
00:33:02,400 --> 00:33:03,240
Qiaoxi.

639
00:33:04,140 --> 00:33:04,980
Come here.

640
00:33:06,240 --> 00:33:07,720
Your birthday's coming up.

641
00:33:07,760 --> 00:33:09,620
Daddy got you a present.

642
00:33:12,320 --> 00:33:13,220
Do you like it?

643
00:33:14,460 --> 00:33:15,780
Black again.

644
00:33:17,220 --> 00:33:18,860
Mom chose it,

645
00:33:18,900 --> 00:33:19,840
or you?

646
00:33:22,080 --> 00:33:24,480
Your mom and I decided together.

647
00:33:25,480 --> 00:33:26,760
Black suits you.

648
00:33:26,800 --> 00:33:27,640
It's a classic look

649
00:33:27,680 --> 00:33:29,240
for a young man.

650
00:33:39,280 --> 00:33:40,280
Qiaoxi.

651
00:33:43,280 --> 00:33:45,300
Dad's swamped with work lately,

652
00:33:45,340 --> 00:33:46,520
so I can't take you there.

653
00:33:47,080 --> 00:33:48,800
The day after tomorrow,
Mom will pick you up.

654
00:34:08,239 --> 00:34:11,320
Happy birthday to you

655
00:34:11,360 --> 00:34:14,179
Happy birthday to you

656
00:34:14,719 --> 00:34:17,760
Happy birthday to you

657
00:34:17,800 --> 00:34:21,120
Happy birthday to you

658
00:34:21,620 --> 00:34:22,520
Jiang Qiaoxi.

659
00:34:22,560 --> 00:34:25,520
Happy birthday to you.

660
00:34:29,739 --> 00:34:32,699
I started collecting these flowers
before winter came.

661
00:34:32,739 --> 00:34:34,460
Mom helped me dry them,

662
00:34:34,500 --> 00:34:35,880
preserved forever,

663
00:34:35,920 --> 00:34:37,880
never to wilt.

664
00:34:38,460 --> 00:34:40,639
But since you love black,

665
00:34:40,679 --> 00:34:43,080
and I've never seen
black flowers in Qunshan.

666
00:34:43,620 --> 00:34:45,239
I dyed them with ink.

667
00:34:45,780 --> 00:34:46,940
Do you think

668
00:34:46,980 --> 00:34:48,100
black looks good?

669
00:34:48,139 --> 00:34:50,380
We don't really like so much black.

670
00:34:50,880 --> 00:34:53,020
But you wear black every day.

671
00:34:53,060 --> 00:34:55,699
Your pencil case, pen, water bottle,

672
00:34:55,739 --> 00:34:57,780
even your eraser all black.

673
00:34:57,820 --> 00:34:59,600
We've never seen

674
00:34:59,640 --> 00:35:00,700
so much black

675
00:35:00,740 --> 00:35:02,140
on one person before.

676
00:35:02,800 --> 00:35:04,740
But Lin Yingtao said,

677
00:35:05,240 --> 00:35:06,380
if you like someone,

678
00:35:06,420 --> 00:35:07,600
you should accept them

679
00:35:07,640 --> 00:35:09,240
just as they are.

680
00:35:09,740 --> 00:35:11,560
I don't mean that kind of likes.

681
00:35:11,600 --> 00:35:12,960
Which kind of likes?

682
00:35:13,460 --> 00:35:14,460
You…

683
00:35:15,160 --> 00:35:16,200
I like it.

684
00:35:20,600 --> 00:35:22,960
Then you can make a statement.

685
00:35:27,360 --> 00:35:28,340
Thank you all.

686
00:35:28,380 --> 00:35:29,860
SMILE, GOOD

687
00:35:29,900 --> 00:35:31,580
Jiang Qiaoxi, make a wish.

688
00:35:34,260 --> 00:35:35,500
Jiang Qiaoxi.

689
00:35:37,100 --> 00:35:38,220
Happy birthday to you.

690
00:35:38,260 --> 00:35:40,740
Du Shang, you're just in time.

691
00:35:40,780 --> 00:35:42,040
We're at the wishing part.

692
00:35:42,080 --> 00:35:43,060
Hurry up.

693
00:35:45,060 --> 00:35:46,140
We've been waiting for you.

694
00:35:46,180 --> 00:35:47,620
It wouldn't be the same without you.

695
00:35:49,120 --> 00:35:49,960
Jiang Qiaoxi.

696
00:35:50,680 --> 00:35:51,880
Happy birthday to you.

697
00:35:53,680 --> 00:35:54,620
Du Shang.

698
00:35:55,380 --> 00:35:56,560
I want to give you

699
00:35:57,260 --> 00:35:58,260
this wish.

700
00:35:58,800 --> 00:35:59,980
Please make a wish.

701
00:36:08,700 --> 00:36:09,600
Quickly.

702
00:36:33,500 --> 00:36:35,040
Jiang Qiaoxi,

703
00:36:35,080 --> 00:36:36,620
never forget

704
00:36:36,660 --> 00:36:37,640
this is your home.

705
00:36:37,680 --> 00:36:38,980
You must come back to us soon.

706
00:36:40,300 --> 00:36:41,220
Yingtao.

707
00:36:41,780 --> 00:36:42,700
Thanks.

708
00:36:43,800 --> 00:36:44,760
Don't thank me.
You're pretty great.

709
00:36:46,280 --> 00:36:48,600
You even gave your birthday wish
to Du Shang.

710
00:36:49,100 --> 00:36:51,220
Who does that?

711
00:36:52,980 --> 00:36:54,840
Anyway, my wish

712
00:36:54,880 --> 00:36:55,920
never came true.

713
00:36:58,540 --> 00:37:01,460
What's your wish?
I'll help you realize it.

714
00:37:02,000 --> 00:37:03,340
Actually…

715
00:37:05,340 --> 00:37:06,400
I don't like black,

716
00:37:07,840 --> 00:37:10,300
but I like the gifts you gave me.

717
00:37:10,800 --> 00:37:11,920
Today,

718
00:37:11,960 --> 00:37:13,280
I like black for the first time.

719
00:37:13,320 --> 00:37:15,240
You don't like black,

720
00:37:15,740 --> 00:37:17,740
then why are all

721
00:37:17,780 --> 00:37:19,140
your clothes, your things black?

722
00:37:19,960 --> 00:37:21,420
The one who likes black

723
00:37:22,060 --> 00:37:23,400
is my brother.

724
00:37:24,760 --> 00:37:26,980
These are the things they bought for me.

725
00:37:27,480 --> 00:37:29,160
They controls and makes me like the color.

726
00:37:29,900 --> 00:37:31,040
I can only like black.

727
00:37:32,960 --> 00:37:35,040
They won't love me for who I am.

728
00:37:38,200 --> 00:37:39,900
So what color do you like?

729
00:37:40,720 --> 00:37:41,960
I didn't think about it,

730
00:37:43,300 --> 00:37:44,320
but

731
00:37:44,820 --> 00:37:45,920
I start to like black.

732
00:37:49,520 --> 00:37:51,800
What else? You can think of something else

733
00:37:51,840 --> 00:37:53,080
and then you will like it.

734
00:37:57,500 --> 00:37:58,600
Red.

735
00:37:58,640 --> 00:37:59,900
I like red.

736
00:38:02,120 --> 00:38:03,040
Jiang Qiaoxi.

737
00:38:03,540 --> 00:38:05,720
When it comes to my birthday,

738
00:38:05,760 --> 00:38:06,600
I'll make a wish for you.

739
00:38:07,440 --> 00:38:09,640
I wish your parents
will love you just the way you are,

740
00:38:09,680 --> 00:38:10,720
okay?

741
00:38:12,160 --> 00:38:13,480
What about you?

742
00:38:14,820 --> 00:38:15,960
What is your wish?

743
00:38:19,580 --> 00:38:21,040
My wish is

744
00:38:22,500 --> 00:38:24,740
that we all stay together

745
00:38:25,240 --> 00:38:26,540
and never leave.

746
00:38:27,600 --> 00:38:29,320
Then keep your wish.

747
00:38:30,480 --> 00:38:31,680
That is more important

748
00:38:32,180 --> 00:38:33,340
to me.

749
00:38:48,340 --> 00:38:51,020
GO TO WORK HAPPILY, RETURN HOME SAFELY.

750
00:39:13,060 --> 00:39:14,740
Qiaoxi, could you get the door?

751
00:39:17,000 --> 00:39:18,340
Yingtao, you're here.

752
00:39:18,380 --> 00:39:20,020
Uncle Jiang,

753
00:39:20,060 --> 00:39:22,060
I bought some fresh shrimp baozi,
would you like some?

754
00:39:22,100 --> 00:39:23,160
Yes.

755
00:39:23,860 --> 00:39:25,000
No.

756
00:39:25,040 --> 00:39:26,680
You can take it back and eat it yourself.

757
00:39:26,720 --> 00:39:27,820
Thank you.

758
00:39:29,720 --> 00:39:32,080
Yingtao, bring it in. Come in.

759
00:39:32,120 --> 00:39:33,400
Bring it in for you to eat?

760
00:39:33,440 --> 00:39:35,720
Who knows what kind of meat
they put in street baozi?

761
00:39:38,080 --> 00:39:39,120
Thank you,

762
00:39:39,160 --> 00:39:40,260
little girl,

763
00:39:40,300 --> 00:39:42,140
but we don't eat street food.

764
00:39:43,100 --> 00:39:44,780
Qiaoxi, close the door.

765
00:39:45,320 --> 00:39:46,620
You're letting the cold air in.

766
00:40:04,540 --> 00:40:06,740
Don't let Yingtao know about this.

767
00:40:07,860 --> 00:40:09,820
Tell her after school starts.

768
00:40:10,320 --> 00:40:12,600
Maybe after not seeing each other
all winter break,

769
00:40:12,640 --> 00:40:14,880
hearing the news will hurt a little less.

770
00:40:15,400 --> 00:40:16,560
It may not be better

771
00:40:17,060 --> 00:40:18,260
after the winter break.

772
00:40:18,760 --> 00:40:20,240
What do you suggest we do then?

773
00:40:20,740 --> 00:40:22,240
This kid

774
00:40:22,780 --> 00:40:25,440
was transferred here and there, on a whim.

775
00:40:36,860 --> 00:40:38,560
Dad, Mom,

776
00:40:39,100 --> 00:40:41,860
who are you saying is transferring away?

777
00:40:42,980 --> 00:40:44,020
It's not Jiang Qiaoxi, right?

778
00:40:44,860 --> 00:40:46,840
He promised he'd come back
after winter break.

779
00:40:47,420 --> 00:40:48,660
He's not a liar.

780
00:40:55,420 --> 00:40:57,240
I'm going to ask him myself.

781
00:40:57,280 --> 00:41:00,320
He promised he'd return after break.

782
00:41:00,360 --> 00:41:03,240
Why would he lie to me?

783
00:41:03,280 --> 00:41:05,620
Yingtao, Aunt Liang has settled

784
00:41:05,660 --> 00:41:07,100
her work matters now.

785
00:41:07,140 --> 00:41:09,100
She just wants to focus on raising Qiaoxi

786
00:41:09,140 --> 00:41:11,040
properly in the provincial capital.

787
00:41:22,240 --> 00:41:23,440
Well…

788
00:41:24,460 --> 00:41:26,000
Then next time…

789
00:41:26,540 --> 00:41:27,760
- Take care.
- Sure.

790
00:41:27,800 --> 00:41:28,880
Next time.

791
00:41:59,780 --> 00:42:01,140
Uncle Wang!

792
00:42:31,060 --> 00:42:31,940
Yingtao.

793
00:42:33,020 --> 00:42:34,380
Study hard.

794
00:42:36,100 --> 00:42:37,600
I mean

795
00:42:39,480 --> 00:42:41,080
grow up to be anything but me.

796
00:43:16,340 --> 00:43:18,480
- Jiang Qiaoxi!
- Jiang Qiaoxi!

797
00:43:18,520 --> 00:43:19,840
Jiang Qiaoxi!

798
00:43:21,120 --> 00:43:22,140
Jiang Qiaoxi!

799
00:43:27,380 --> 00:43:28,880
Jiang Qiaoxi!

800
00:43:28,920 --> 00:43:31,480
Jiang Qiaoxi, write to me.

801
00:43:31,520 --> 00:43:33,020
You must write to me.

802
00:43:33,060 --> 00:43:34,560
Yingtao!

803
00:43:34,600 --> 00:43:36,720
I'll be back after winter break!

804
00:43:36,760 --> 00:43:38,140
Yingtao!

805
00:43:38,180 --> 00:43:40,040
I'll be back after winter break!

806
00:43:47,480 --> 00:43:48,540
I know.

807
00:43:49,980 --> 00:43:51,440
No matter how brave I am,

808
00:43:52,980 --> 00:43:54,480
I'll never grow wings.

809
00:44:13,660 --> 00:44:14,900
Dad says

810
00:44:15,400 --> 00:44:16,420
living is like

811
00:44:16,920 --> 00:44:18,000
being a silkworm,

812
00:44:18,500 --> 00:44:20,380
a snake, or a crab.

813
00:44:21,640 --> 00:44:23,020
When the time comes,

814
00:44:23,060 --> 00:44:25,060
you must step out of the old shell.

815
00:44:25,560 --> 00:44:27,500
Only by forgetting certain things

816
00:44:27,540 --> 00:44:28,480
and moving on,

817
00:44:29,160 --> 00:44:30,760
you can travel light

818
00:44:31,400 --> 00:44:33,620
and live better.

819
